cally%20knocking%20on%20the%20doors%20and%20entering%20the%2012th-century%20landmark%20which%20has%20been%20restored%20after%20a%20devastating%20fire%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWearing%20new%20designer%20vestments%20and%20carrying%20a%20staff%20cut%20from%20one%20of%20the%20roof%20beams%20that%20survived%20the%20inferno%2C%20Laurent%20Ulrich%20joined%20hundreds%20of%20VIPs%20inside%20the%20Gothic%20masterpiece%20for%20a%20two-hour%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUlrich%20commanded%20the%20cathedral%20to%20%26quot%3Bopen%20your%20doors%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20entered%20the%20magnificently-restored%20edifice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20sat%20on%20the%20front%20row%20as%20guest%20of%20honour%20next%20to%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20with%20invitees%20marvelling%20at%20the%20freshly%20cleaned%20walls%2C%20new%20furniture%20and%20state-of-the-art%20lightening%20installed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20cathedral's%20overhaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20small%20crowds%20of%20Parisians%20and%20tourists%20braved%20wet%20weather%20and%20high%20winds%20to%20witness%20the%20renaissance%20of%20a%20beloved%20monument%20which%20came%20close%20to%20being%20totally%20destroyed%20by%20the%20inferno%20that%20toppled%20its%20roof%20and%20spire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20really%20beautiful%2C%20even%20more%20so%20now%20that%20the%20spire%20has%20been%20restored%2C%26quot%3B%20Marie%20Jean%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20dentist%20from%20southwest%20France%2C%20told%20AFP%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reconstruction%20effort%20has%20cost%20around%20700%20million%20euros%20(%24750%20million)%2C%20financed%20from%20donations%2C%20with%20the%20re-opening%20achieved%20within%20a%20five-year%20deadline%20set%20by%20Macron%20despite%20predictions%20it%20could%20take%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20had%20to%20overcome%20problems%20with%20lead%20pollution%2C%20the%20Covid-19%20epidemic%2C%20and%20the%20army%20general%20overseeing%20the%20project%20falling%20to%20his%20death%20while%20hiking%20in%20the%20Pyrenees%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20cathedral%20like%20we%20have%20never%20seen%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Philippe%20Jost%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20project%20manager%20last%20year%2C%20told%20Franceinfo%20radio%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20proud%20to%20%26quot%3Bshow%20the%20whole%20world%26quot%3B%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20collective%20success%20and%20a%20source%20of%20pride%20for%20all%20of%20France%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaturday's%20service%20will%20feature%20prayer%2C%20organ%20music%20and%20hymns%20from%20the%20cathedral's%20choir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20public%20concert%20planned%20in%20front%20of%20the%20cathedral%20featuring%20Chinese%20piano%20virtuoso%20Lang%20Lang%20and%20possibly%20US%20singer%20and%20fashion%20designer%20Pharrell%20Williams%20had%20to%20be%20pre-recorded%20on%20Friday%20night%20because%20of%20the%20stormy%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Do%20the%20impossible'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeld%20up%20as%20an%20example%20of%20French%20creativity%20and%20resilience%20by%20Macron%2C%20Notre%20Dame's%20renaissance%20so%20soon%20after%20the%20fire%20comes%20at%20a%20difficult%20time%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sense%20of%20national%20accomplishment%20in%20restoring%20a%20symbol%20of%20Paris%20has%20been%20undercut%20by%20political%20turmoil%20that%20has%20left%20France%20without%20a%20proper%20government%20since%20last%20week%20when%20prime%20minister%20Michel%20Barnier%20lost%20a%20confidence%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20is%20hoping%20the%20re-opening%20might%20provide%20a%20fleeting%20sense%20of%20national%20pride%20and%20unity%20--%20as%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20did%20in%20July%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20immense%20security%20operation%20also%20recalls%20the%20Olympics%20--%20with%20some%206%2C000%20police%20officers%20and%20gendarmes%20mobilised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20re-opening%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20proof%20that%20we%20know%20how%20to%20do%20grand%20things%2C%20we%20know%20how%20to%20do%20the%20impossible%26quot%3B%20Macron%20said%20Thursday%20in%20a%20televised%20address%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20set%20to%20address%20the%20congregation%20during%20Saturday's%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20show%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20has%20scored%20a%20major%20coup%20by%20attracting%20incoming%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20for%20his%20first%20foreign%20trip%20since%20his%20re-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2040%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%20are%20also%20present%2C%20including%20Ukrainian%20leader%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%2C%20who%20was%20given%20a%20round%20of%20applause%20as%20he%20entered%20Notre%20Dame%2C%20as%20well%20as%20British%20heir%20to%20the%20throne%2C%20Prince%20William.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20hosted%20three-way%20talks%20with%20Zelensky%20and%20Trump%20at%20the%20presidential%20palace%20shortly%20before%20the%20ceremony%2C%20with%20future%20US%20military%20support%20for%20Ukraine's%20war%20effort%20against%20Russia's%20invasion%20expected%20to%20have%20been%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20vowed%20to%20force%20an%20end%20to%20the%20nearly%20three-year%20Ukraine%20war%20when%20he%20takes%20office%2C%20sparking%20fears%20in%20Kyiv%20that%20he%20will%20force%20Ukraine%20to%20make%20territorial%20concessions%20to%20Russia%20which%20Zelensky%20is%20resisting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20the%20world%20is%20going%20a%20little%20crazy%20right%20now%20and%20we%20will%20be%20talking%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20sit%20down%20for%20talks%20with%20Macron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20surprising%20absentee%20on%20Saturday%20was%20Pope%20Francis%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Catholic%20Church.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sent%20a%20message