20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%2C%20and%20not%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20always%20held%20to%20the%20view%20that%20this%20war%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20solved%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20people%20are%20going%20to%20return%20to%20some%20kind%20of%20negotiating%20table%2C%20the%20sooner%20the%20better.%20Our%20effort%20has%20been%20to%20facilitate%20that%20to%20the%20extent%20possible.%20That%20has%20not%20been%20the%20most%20popular%20thing%2C%20at%20least%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20at%20the%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Minister%20further%20emphasised%20that%20the%20world%20is%20accepting%20the%20reality%20of%20negotiation%20rather%20than%20continuing%20the%20war.%20He%20further%20pointed%20out%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20encourage%20a%20resolution%20to%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20today%2C%20the%20needle%20is%20moving%20more%20towards%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20negotiation%20than%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20war...We%20are%20going%20to%20Moscow%2C%20talking%20to%20President%20Putin%2C%20going%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20engaging%20President%20Zelensky%2C%20meeting%20them%20in%20other%20places%2C%20trying%20to%20see%20if%20we%20can%20encourage%20find%20common%20threads%20that%20can%20be%20picked%20up%20at%20some%20point%20in%20time%20when%20the%20circumstances%20are%20right%20to%20be%20developed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%2C%20however%2C%20also%20clarified%20that%20India%20does%20not%20have%20a%20'peace%20plan'%20to%20resolve%20the%20conflict%2C%20but%20holds%20%26quot%3Bhonest%20and%20transparent%26quot%3B%20conversations%20between%20both%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20attempting%20a%20peace%20plan%2C%20we're%20not%20doing%20a%20mediation%20in%20that%20sense.%20We're%20doing%20multiple%20conversations%20and%20are%20very%20transparent%20about%20telling%20each%20party%20that%20the%20end%20of%20conversation%20that%20this%20is%20what%20we'll%20tell%20the%20other%20party.%20We%20think%20that%20at%20this%20point%20of%20time%2C%20the%20most%20useful...diplomatically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%20that%20he%20believed%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20bring%20the%20Global%20South's%20perspective%20on%20how%20they%20are%20impacted%20by%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20believe%20in%20this%20that%20we%20articulate%20the%20sentiments%20and%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20global%20South%2C%20125%20other%20countries%20who%20found%20their%20fuel%20costs%2C%20food%20costs%2C%20inflation%2C%20their%20fertilizer%20cost%20impacted%20by%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20is%20on%20an%20official%20visit%20to%20Qatar%20and%20Bahrain%20from%20December%206-9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bahrain%2C%20he%20will%20co-chair%20the%204th%20India-Bahrain%20High%20Joint%20Commission%20(HJC)%20with%20the%20Foreign%20Minister%20of%20Bahrain%2C%20Abdullatif%20bin%20Rashid%20Al%20Zayani.%20EAM%20will%20also%20participate%20in%20the%2020th%20edition%20of%20IISS%20Manama%20Dialogue%20in%20Bahrain%20on%20December%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20met%20Qatari%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Sheikh%20Faisal%20bin%20Thani%20bin%20Faisal%20Al%20Thani%20and%20Minister%20of%20State%2C%20Ahmed%20Al%20Sayed%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Doha%20Forum.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20leaders%20were%20seen%20shaking%20hands%20and%20holding%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPleased%20to%20meet%20Qatari%20Minister%20of%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Industry%20Sheikh%20Faisal%20bin%20Thani%20bin%20Faisal%20Al%20Thani%20and%20MoS%20Ahmed%20Al%20Sayed%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Doha%20Forum%20today%2C%2