22author%22%3A%22CHAITANYA%20MARPAKWAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fmaharashtra-assembly-speaker-election-mva-may-not-challenge-requests-deputy-speaker-post%2Farticleshow%2F116085343.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%2C%20Zelensky%2C%20Macron%20Discuss%20%26quot%3BCrazy%26quot%3B%20World%20In%20Paris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20on%20Saturday%20hosted%20three-way%20talks%20with%20Ukrainian%20counterpart%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20and%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20discussing%20what%20the%20American%20president-elect%20termed%20a%20world%20that%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Blittle%20crazy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky's%20meeting%20with%20Trump%20just%20before%20the%20three%20men%20headed%20to%20Notre%20Dame%20for%20the%20re-opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%20great%20Paris%20cathedral%20was%20his%20first%20face-to-face%20meeting%20with%20tycoon-turned-politician%20since%20his%20election%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20of%20huge%20importance%20to%20Zelensky%20given%20the%20fears%20in%20Kyiv%20that%20Trump%2C%20who%20once%20boasted%20he%20could%20end%20Russia's%20war%20on%20Ukraine%20in%2024%20hours%2C%20may%20urge%20Ukraine%20to%20make%20concessions%20to%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20offered%20a%20unique%20chance%20for%20Macron%20to%20gain%20insights%20into%20how%20a%20second%20Trump%20presidency%20will%20shape%20out%20when%20he%20takes%20office%20in%20January%2C%20with%20the%20trip%20to%20Paris%20his%20first%20international%20visit%20since%20the%20election%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20Macron%20embraced%20and%20shook%20hands%20several%20times%20on%20the%20steps%20of%20the%20French%20presidential%20palace%2C%20with%20Trump%20given%20a%20full%20guard%20of%20honour%20despite%20not%20yet%20being%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20the%20world%20is%20going%20a%20little%20crazy%20right%20now%20and%20we%20will%20be%20talking%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20reporters%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20sit%20down%20for%20the%20talks%20with%20Macron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20men%20during%20his%20first%20term%2C%20Trump%20hailed%20his%20ties%20with%20the%20centrist%20French%20leader%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20great%20relationship%20as%20everyone%20knows.%20We%20accomplished%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Remember%20the%20solidarity'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20told%20Trump%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20great%20honour%20for%20French%20people%20to%20welcome%20you%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20re-opening%20ceremony%20at%20Notre%20Dame%2C%20which%20was%20devastated%20by%20a%20blaze%20in%202019%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20were%20president%20at%20that%20time%20and%20I%20remember%20the%20solidarity%20and%20the%20immediate%20reaction%2C%26quot%3B%20Macron%20added%2C%20speaking%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20first%20took%20office%20in%202017%2C%20Trump's%20ties%20with%20Macron%20--%20then%20also%20a%20fresh%20face%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20--%20began%20warmly%20despite%20their%20obvious%20political%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20long%20and%20muscular%20handshakes%20--%20which%20saw%20each%20man%20seek%20to%20assert%20his%20superiority%20--%20became%20a%20light-hearted%20focus%20of%20attention%20before%20ties%20cooled%2C%20then%20soured%2C%20following%20disputes%20about%20climate%20change%2C%20trade%20and%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20expected%20to%20discuss%20the%20wars%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20as%20well%20as%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20earlier%20wrote%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform%20that%20the%20United%20States%20should%20%26quot%3Bnot%20get%20involved%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20situation%20in%20Syria%2C