oi%20wajah%20hi%20toh%20nahi%20thi.%20Bina%20wajah%20ke%20talaq%20diya%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(There%20was%20no%20reason%20at%20all.%20He%20divorced%20me%20without%20a%20reason)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nida%2C%20who%20uses%20a%20single%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20'talaq'%20means%20divorce%20in%20Arabic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversial%20practice%20of%20'triple%20talaq'%20that%20allows%20Muslim%20men%20to%20divorce%20their%20wives%20instantly%20by%20saying%20'talaq'%20thrice%20was%20banned%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202017.%20The%20top%20court%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B.%20In%202019%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20also%20approved%20a%20bill%20outlawing%20the%20centuries-old%20right%20of%20a%20Muslim%20man%20to%20instantly%20divorce%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENida%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Moradabad%2C%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20her%20husband%2C%20Ejazul%2C%20for%20divorcing%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20watching%20a%20video%20because%20I%20had%20to%20visit%20Sambhal%20for%20a%20wedding.%20I%20also%20had%20some%20personal%20work.%20So%20I%20was%20checking%20if%20it%20was%20safe%20to%20go%20there.%20My%20husband%20asked%20me%20why%20I%20was%20watching%20the%20video.%20I%20said%20what%20is%20wrong%20is%20wrong.%20Everyone%20has%20the%20right%20to%20defend%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nida%2C%20elaborating%20on%20what%20started%20the%20fight%20between%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUpon%20hearing%20this%2C%20he%20said%20you%20are%20not%20a%20Muslim%3B%20you%20are%20an%20infidel.%20You%20support%20police.%20He%20started%20misbehaving%20with%20me.%20He%20said%20I%20will%20not%20keep%20you%20anymore%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20you%20do%20and%20pronounced%20triple%20talaq.%20He%20then%20said%20he%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Nida%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20black%20burqa%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2