tion%20with%20India%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20but%20added%20that%20he%20would%20always%20stand%20up%20for%20himself%2C%20as%20day%20two%20of%20the%20pink%20ball%20Test%20saw%20the%20hosts%20tighten%20their%20grip%20on%20the%20game.%20Siraj%20gave%20a%20fiery%20send-off%20to%20Head%2C%20who%20struck%20his%20second%20Test%20century%20against%20India%20and%20eighth%20overall.%20Head%20made%20a%20brisk%20140%20off%20141%20balls%2C%20which%20put%20Australia%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%20to%20level%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20actually%20jokingly%20said%20'well%20bowled'%20and%20then%20he%20pointed%20me%20in%20(to%20go%20to)%20the%20shades.%20I%20had%20my%20reaction%20as%20well%20but%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20give%20(it)%20too%20much%20airtime%2C%26quot%3B%20Head%20told%20the%20media%20after%20the%20end%20of%20play%20on%20day%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20unfolded%20after%20Siraj%2C%20having%20dropped%20the%20local%20hero%20on%2076%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20conceded%20a%20six%20to%20him.%20The%20Hyderabadi%20responded%20immediately%2C%20castling%20Head%20with%20a%20low%20full%20toss%20and%20celebrating%20animatedly%2C%20while%20instructing%20him%20to%20walk%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20surprised%20at%20the%20reaction%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20situation%20of%20the%20game%20and%20the%20lead%20up%20and%20there%20was%20no%20confrontation%20leading%20up%20to%20it%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20probably%2C%20a%20little%20bit%20far%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20I'm%20disappointed%20in%20the%20reaction%20that%20I%20gave%20back%20but%20I'm%20also%20going%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20myself.%20I'd%20like%20to%20think%20in%20our%20team%20that%20we%20wouldn't%20do%20that%2C%20it's%20not%20how%20I'd%20like%20to%20play%20the%20game%20and%20I'd%20feel%20like%20my%20teammates%20(are)%20the%20same%20and%20if%20I'd%20seen%20that%20in%20that%2