0were%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20India%20has%20never%20been%20for%20de-dollarisation%2C%20right%20now%20there%20is%20no%20proposal%20to%20have%20a%20BRICS%20currency.%20The%20BRICS%20do%20discuss%20financial%20transactions...%20The%20US%20is%20our%20largest%20trade%20partner%2C%20we%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20weakening%20the%20dollar%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20warning%20BRICS%20members%20to%20not%20commit%20to%20creating%20a%20new%20currency%20or%20supporting%20another%20currency%20that%20would%20replace%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20had%20said%20they%20can%20go%20find%20another%20'sucker'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20require%20a%20commitment%20from%20these%20countries%20that%20they%20will%20neither%20create%20a%20new%20BRICS%20currency%2C%20nor%20back%20any%20other%20currency%20to%20replace%20the%20mighty%20US%20Dollar%20or%2C%20they%20will%20face%20100%20per%20cent%20tariffs%2C%20and%20should%20expect%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20selling%20into%20the%20wonderful%20US%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20go%20find%20another%20'sucker'.%20There%20is%20no%20chance%20that%20the%20BRICS%20will%20replace%20the%20US%20dollar%20in%20international%20trade%2C%20and%20any%20country%20that%20tries%20should%20wave%20goodbye%20to%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20President-elect%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733584380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F20q8dn1o_s-jaishankar_625x300_07_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-proposal-for-brics-currency-s-jaishankar-after-trumps-tariff-warning-7195662%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20start%20a%20new%20currency%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said%20in%20Qatar%2C%20where%20he%20has%20gone%20to%20attend%20the%20Doha%20Forum.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-proposal-for-brics-currency-s-jaishankar-after-trumps-tariff-warning-7195662%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Who%20Shot%20At%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20%26quot%3BGem%20Of%20The%20Nation%26quot%3B%3A%20Minister's%20Dig%20At%20Akalis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Ravneet%20Singh%20Bittu%20has%20suggested%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20should%20honour%20the%20man%20who%20shot%20at%20Akali%20Dal%20chief%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Badal%20since%20he%20himself%20had%20accepted%20he%20committed%20sacrilege%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20former%20Punjab%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20had%20to%20serve%20penance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bittu%20in%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20also%20suggested%20the%20party's%20general%20secretary%20Bikram%20Singh%20Majithia%20should%20embrace%20Narain%20Singh%20Chaura%2C%20the%20man%20who%20shot%20at%20Mr%20Badal%2C%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20same%20way%20Majithia%20had%20embraced%20Beant%20Singh's%20killers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bittu%20alleged%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20sympathised%20with%20terrorists%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20terrorists%20are%20not%20loyal%20to%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20should%20show%20respect%20to%20Narain%20Singh%20Chaura.%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20Jathedar%20to%20honour%20Narain%20Singh%20Chaura%20by%20putting%20his%20picture%20in%20the%20museum%20built%20next%20to%20the%20Akal%20Takht%20Sahib%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bittu%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Railway%20and%20Food%20Processing%20Industries%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Beant%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20was%20assassinated%20by%20a%20suicide%20bomber%20in%20August%201995.%3C%2