experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20couldn't%20believe%20how%20much%20the%20restaurant%20resembled%20the%20show's%20set.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223325%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20busy%20restaurant%20with%20an%20open%20kitchen.%20The%20left%20half%20of%20the%20kitchen%20has%20red%20decor%20and%20the%20right%20half%20has%20blue%20decor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f3910e45a68623a279254%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20was%20visible%20from%20the%20dining%20area%20and%20had%20chefs%20broken%20up%20into%20red%20and%20blue%20%26quot%3Bteams.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Pitera%20Statile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20restaurant%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20by%20how%20familiar%20the%20main%20dining%20area%20looked.%20I%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20had%20stumbled%20onto%20the%20set%20of%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20restaurant's%20website%2C%20emulating%20the%20show%20was%20intentional.%20The%20kitchen%2C%20which%20was%20visible%20from%20the%20dining%20area%2C%20even%20had%20chefs%20broken%20up%20into%20red%20and%20blue%20%26quot%3Bteams%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20on%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20subtle%20theming%20was%20everywhere.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223578%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20hold%20half-full%20Champagne%20glasses%20garnished%20with%20strawberries%20on%20pitchfork-themed%20toothpicks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f394f9e9761932b4a59a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20show's%20signature%20pitchforks%20were%20even%20on%20our%20drinks.%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Pitera%20Statile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20ate%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20as%20part%20of%20our%20anniversary%20celebration%2C%20so%20we%20we