3Cstrong%3EApril%2025%2C%202024%3A%20Straub%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Fleming%20in%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStraub's%20complaint%20said%20Fleming%20had%20never%20been%20an%20%26quot%3Bowner%26quot%3B%20of%20any%20Miss%20America%20entity%20and%20sued%20her%20for%20breach%20of%20fiduciary%20duties%20and%20obligations%2C%20%26quot%3Bat%20will%26quot%3B%20employment%20agreement%2C%20temporary%20and%20permanent%20injunctive%20relief%2C%20and%20trademark%20infringement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20complaint%20sought%20%2420%20million%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225421161f-3e23-480a-96f4-b05e716f345c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EApril%2029%2C%202024%3A%20Straub%20said%20he%20was%20Miss%20America's%20owner%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20staffers.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStraub%20sent%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faccessglobal.media.clients.ellingtoncms.com%2Fuploads%2Ffroala_editor%2Ffiles%2Fstraub%2520email.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Miss%20America%20directors%20and%20licensees%20in%20late%20December%202022%20stating%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bpurchased%20all%20the%20assets%20of%20the%20former%20Miss%20America%20Organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20hired%20Fleming%20to%20run%20Miss%20America%20and%20terminated%20her%20%26quot%3Bafter%20we%20received%20damaging%20information%20and%20conducted%20an%20extensive%20audit%20of%20her%20conduct%20while%20working%20with%20the%20organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20letter%2C%20Krebs%20and%20other%20former%20Miss%20America%20board%20members%20told%20licensees%20and%20directors%20via%20email%20they%20had%20%26quot%3Bvoted%20unanimously%20to%20transfer%20the%20assets%20to%20Robin%20Fleming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStraub%20also%20hosted%20Zoom%20meetings%20with%20Miss%20America%20licensees%20and%20contractual%20partners%20in%20May%2C%20during%20which%20he%20said%20he%20was%20Miss%20America's%20owner%20and%20had%20fired%20Fleming%20as%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235c60f3e-4943-430f-ac46-9c85f16996cd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJuly%2029%2C%202024%3A%20Straub%20said%20he%20planned%20to%20file%20for%20bankruptcy%20on%20Miss%20America's%20behalf.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20court%20docket%20reviewed%20by%20BI%2C%20Straub%20and%20Fleming%20were%20ordered%20to%20hold%20a%20%26quot%3Bconciliation%20conference%26quot%3B%20to%20discuss%20his%20state-level%20lawsuit%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20lawsuit%2C%20Fleming%20said%20Straub%20used%20the%20meeting%20to%20%26quot%3Bdirectly%20threaten%2C%20intimidate%20and%20extort%26quot%3B%20her.%20She%20said%20Straub%20told%20her%20he%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bshut%20down%20Miss%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20called%20himself%20%26quot%3BHamas%26quot%3B%20and%20Fleming%20%26quot%3BIsrael%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20was%20Hitler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20complaint%20also%20said%20that%20Straub%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bintended%20to%20file%20for%20bankruptcy%20on%20behalf%20of%20her%20Miss%20America%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a016da0-f8d6-431d-8c2c-574ed77834c7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFall%20of%202024%3A%20Fleming%20said%20Straub%20made%20defamatory%20statements%20about%20her%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFleming%20said%20Straub%20sent%20additional%20letters%20to%20state%20executive%20directors%20in%20September%20saying%20he%20had%20fired%20her%2C%20and%2C%20in%20November%202024%2C%20he%20publicly%20said%20she%20was%20funding%20her%20legal%20defense%20through%20Miss%20America's%20scholarship%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20suit%20described%20his%20statements%20as%20defamatory%20and%20led%20to%20potential%20business%20deals%20to%20fall%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20complaint%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Borganizers%20of%20the%20iconic%20Macy's%20Thanksgiving%20parade%20withdrew%20their%20invitation%20to%20have%2