C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20fly%20to%20our%20vacation%20destinations%20at%20half-price%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%2C%20now%20ages%205%20and%207%2C%20have%20traveled%20extensively%20around%20the%20U.S.%20Our%20Delta%20Platinum%20cards%20have%20made%20that%20possible.%20Each%20year%2C%20we%20use%20our%20companion%20passes%20to%20take%20a%20family%20vacation.%20We%20have%20been%20to%20Charleston%20once%20and%20Florida%20several%20times%20with%20them%20on%20these%20passes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20signed%20up%2C%20the%20annual%20fee%20was%20only%20%24250.%20We%20justified%20this%20price%20because%20regardless%20of%20where%20we%20flew%20with%20Delta%2C%20we%20weren't%20spending%20less%20than%20%24250%20on%20a%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmex%20recently%20increased%20the%20annual%20fee%20for%20the%20Delta%20Platinum%20to%20%24350%2Fyear%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20good%20value%20to%20us.%20The%20higher%20annual%20fee%20now%20allows%20you%20to%20use%20the%20companion%20pass%20for%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20Central%20America%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20Alaska%2C%20whereas%20before%2C%20it%20only%20covered%20the%20lower%2048%20states.%20Since%20we%20live%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20we%20always%20have%20a%20warm%20winter%20getaway%20on%20our%20list%20for%20the%20winter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20other%20perks%20offer%20added%20value%2C%20even%20if%20they%20aren't%20our%20top%20priority%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Delta%20Platinum%20card%20also%20offers%20other%20perks%20like%20discounted%20ticket%20bookings%20and%20additional%20points%20toward%20Medallion%20status.%20It%20also%20offers%20several%20statement%20credits%20you%20can%20enroll%20in%2C%20including%20%2410%20a%20month%20in%20rideshare%20credits%2C%20%2410%20a%20month%20Resy%20credits%2C%20and%20a%20%24150%20Delta%20Stays%20credit%20when%20using%20your%20credit%20card%20to%20book%20through%20the%20Delta%20Stays%20platform%20on%20delta.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20have%20yet%20to%20use%20the%20Delta%20Stays%20credit%2C%20I