rs%20made%20from%20recycled%20material.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20help%20in%20reducing%20landfill%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20pavers%20can%20also%20support%20vegetation%2C%20contributing%20to%20greener%20urban%20environments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20green%20pavers%20are%20versatile%20to%20work%20with%20and%20add%20depth%20and%20dimension%20to%20the%20space%2C%20Vivek%20says%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20to%20keep%20in%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20green%20pavers%2C%20architects%20need%20to%20design%20effective%20drainage%20systems.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20recycled%20raw%20material%20should%20be%20locally%20sourced%20so%20as%20to%20minimise%20the%20environmental%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Orient%20stranded%20board%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20age%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337009%2Fecofriendly-mud-house-near-chennai-traditional-nalukketu-architecture-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodular%20building%20techniques%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20starting%20to%20gain%20popularity%2C%20the%20orient%20stranded%20boards%20provide%20ample%20scope%20for%20experimentation.%20A%20type%20of%20engineered%20wood%20panel%20made%20from%20wood%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin%2C%20they%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Aameer%20Chauhan%2C%20Sustainability%20Manager%20at%20Edifice%20Consultant%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20an%20award-winning%20architecture%20design%20firm%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COrient%20stranded%20board%20(OSB)%20has%20a%20low%20embodied%20carbon%20value%20and%20can%20be%20easily%2