_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-383824%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECreating%20a%20dynamic%20and%20encouraging%20environment%20to%20make%20learning%20a%20better%20experience%20for%20children%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESABIA%20believes%20in%20building%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%20where%20individuals%20come%20with%20the%20heart%20and%20intention%20of%20helping%2C%20and%20volunteers%20form%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20operations.%20In%202024%20alone%2C%20they%20had%20a%20team%20of%20200%20volunteers%20who%20worked%20with%20and%20were%20able%20to%20enrich%20the%20reading%20experience%20for%20over%20500%20students%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBackend%20to%20frontend%2C%20everything%20is%20done%20by%20volunteers.%20We%20have%20a%20core%20team%2C%20but%20only%20two%20of%20us%20are%20full-time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20reached%20over%2030%2C000%20children%20across%20175%20schools%20in%2016%20states.%20The%20group%E2%80%99s%20community%20libraries%20in%20cities%20like%20Kota%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20Delhi%2C%20housing%20more%20than%205%2C000%20books%2C%20recently%20welcomed%20232