0as%20an%20end-of-term%20payout%2C%20encouraging%20long-term%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20customers%20are%20provided%20with%20a%20proper%20breed%20certificate%20of%20the%20cow%20and%20its%20genetic%20parents%20to%20ensure%20the%20purity%20of%20the%20breed.%20In%20fact%2C%20customers%20are%20welcome%20to%20meet%20their%20pet%20cow%20whenever%20they%20wish.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20able%20to%20play%20with%20%3Cem%3ERadha%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20farm%2C%20and%20the%20feeling%20of%20owning%20a%20cow%20is%20something%20unexplainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Simple%20H%20Singh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFulfilling%20urban%20needs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20customers%20like%20Puspanjali%20Dutta%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Cow%20Currency%E2%80%99%20model%20rekindles%20childhood%20memories.%20%E2%80%9CI%20missed%20drinking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fis-your-milk-adulterated-shorts-food-foodsafety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epure%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20moving%20to%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%20have%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20drinking%20milk%20from%20my%20own%20cow%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20named%20Rivan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20urban%20cities%20do%20not%20have%20the%20time%20or%20space%20to%20care%20for%20the%20cow.%20This%20model%20fulfils%20that%20in%20the%20best%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Puspanjali%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimple%2C%20who%20has%20Celiac%20disease%2C%20highlights%20the%20product%E2%80%99s%20health%20benefits.%20%E2%80%9CPackaged%20milk%20always%20causes%20allergic%20reactions%20for%20me.%20But%20for%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20no%20issues%20with%20their%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E