e%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vimlendu%20Jha%2C%20an%20environmentalist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Swechha%2C%20a%20youth-run%20NGO%20that%20focuses%20on%20environmental%20issues%20and%20education.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20baseline%20for%20pollution%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20is%20high%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20almost%20always%20above%20250.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20Delhi%20is%20not%20the%20only%20city%20battling%20pollution.%20The%20Indian%20subcontinent%2C%20including%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Nepal%2C%20hosts%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20polluted%20cities%2C%20far%20exceeding%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20safe%20limit%20of%2050%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%C2%B3%20for%20particulate%20matter%20(a%20mixture%20of%20solid%20particles%20and%20liquid%20droplets%20in%20the%20air).%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20have%20private%20solutions%20to%20public%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAir%20pollution%20can%20only%20be%20solved%20if%20there%20is%20a%20collective%20solution%20found%20to%20this%2C%20not%20necessarily%20by%20citizens%20alone%2C%20but%20by%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%203941px)%20100vw%2C%203941px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223941%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cricket%20player%20on%20a%20field%20obscured%20by%20heavy%20smog%20and%20air%20pollution%2C%20reducing%20visibility.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621.jpeg%203941w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621-240x300.jpeg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621-500x625.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621-768x960.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621-1229x1536.jpeg%201229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621-1638x2048.jpeg%201638w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621-1200x1500.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona_11zon-1732804621-150x188.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384041%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224927%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20baseline%20for%20pollution%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20is%20high%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20almost%20always%20above%20250.%E2%80%9D%20Vimlendu%20Jha%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E(Representational%20image)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20government%20has%20made%20some%20strides%20in%20addressing%20pollution%2C%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333727%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-aqi-entrepreneurs-innovations-prevent-stubble-burning-farmers-smog-punjab-haryana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estubble%20burning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20vehicular%20pollution%2C%20and%20construction%20dust%2C%20but%20coal-burning%20power%20plants%20continue%20to%20operate%20without%20proper%20regulatory%20measures.%20%E2%80%9CThe